cs.MM, cs.SD, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper proposes a method for speaker diarization in TV series by combining audio and video modalities. This involves using machine learning techniques for speech recognition, image processing, and data matching. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.MM (Multimedia), followed by cs.SD (Sound), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
